---
title: Classic Homestyle Spaghetti & Meatballs with Tomato Sauce & Parmesan
description: Savory and satisfying, spaghetti and meatballs is a crowd-pleasing gold standard. Tender, garlicky beef meatballs infused with Parmesan cheese and Italian spices roast in the oven till browned on the outside and juicy on the inside. They’re tossed in a rich marinara sauce with al dente spaghetti and a final flourish of Parmesan (cause we’re not messing with this classic!).
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66313af70fc5c011176b0d56-46bef013.jpeg
